    "Based on the correctly assigned entries (hits), F₁-score (Call-Accuracy) are calculated according to classic information retrieval metrics.",
    "In a second step, the natural answer generated by the agent was manually checked for content correctness and coherence.",
    "This evaluation is referred to as Answer-Accuracy.",
    "The other tools are implicitly evaluated using these methods.",
    "This demonstrates an average Tool-Accuracy of 0.86, a Call-Accuracy of 0.852, and an Answer-Accuracy of 0.61 (Table 1)."
